# Clean product URLs — e.g. /vogue → product.html?slug=vogue
# Only match single-segment paths (no slashes after the first one).
# Known static files (index.html, product.html, etc.) are served first by CF Pages.
# Functions at /api/* are handled by Cloudflare Pages file-based routing.
# The :slug placeholder matches a single path segment (no nested paths).
/:slug  /product.html?slug=:slug  200
